Package com.clarionmedia.infinitum.di.impl

Provides concrete implementations for the DI framework.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AutowiredBeanPostProcessor
    Implementation of BeanPostProcessor used to inject autowired bean dependencies after beans have been initialized.
    ConfigurableBeanFactory
    Implementation of BeanFactory for storing beans that have been configured in infinitum.cfg.xml.
    GenericBeanDefinitionBuilder
    Generic implementation of BeanDefinitionBuilder.
    ObjectInjector
    Implementation of ActivityInjector for injecting Android resources and framework components into any object.
    PrototypeBeanDefinition
    Concrete implementation of AbstractBeanDefinition which describes prototype beans.
    SingletonBeanDefinition
    Concrete implementation of AbstractBeanDefinition which describes singleton beans.
